  }, "Table 1: Structure of the online master's course in data science (University of Essex Online, 2022a).")), mdx("p", null, "Van der Aalst (2014) provides a visualisation containing nine subdisciplines representing the profile of a data scientist. Based on the course description, Figure 2 combines the perceived focus areas and Van der Aalst's subdisciplines. The goal is to identify focus areas, not to compare with other universities."), mdx("p", null, mdx("img", {
